These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, february, november, march
House: cape-cod, victorian, farmhouse, gothic-revival
The people have 4 different jobs:  manager, chef, software-developer, social-worker
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, daisy, rose, dahlia
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, guinea-pig, horse, mouse
 1. the manager is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 2. the victorian house is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 3. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
 4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 5. the person who growsazalea is the person who's birthday is in december##1
 6. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 7. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
 9. the software-developer is the person who's birthday is in december##1
10. the owner of the horse is the chef##1
11. the cape-cod house is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Birthday          | february    | november      | december  | march     |
| House         | gothic-revival    | farmhouse   | cape-cod | victorian      |
| Job   | chef       | manager | software-developer     | social-worker    |
| Flower   | dahlia | daisy         | azalea  | rose    |
| Pet           | horse      | mouse       | chinchilla | guinea-pig |

