.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-2::.
4 different games are played: go, whist, scrabble, canasta
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, drama, satire, spy
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, aconite, amaryllis, daisy
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, german, spanish, canadian
There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, mauve, amber, orange
 1. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
 2. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
 3. the person who likes orange is on the right of the canadian##1
 4. the person playing canasta is on the far right##1
 5. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing whist##1
 6. the person who likes amber is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
 7. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 8. the german is the person who growsdaisy##1
 9. the person watching satire movies is the person who growsamaryllis##1
10. the person who growsrose is on the far right##1
11. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the thai##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |       4       |
| Game      | whist      | go     | scrabble    | canasta |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | drama   | satire   | spy           |
| Flower   | aconite  | daisy     | amaryllis    | rose         |
| Nationality           | canadian         | german | spanish     | thai        |
| Color         | aquamarine     | orange  | mauve | amber       |

