.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-3::.
City: rome, hamburg, berlin, prague
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, writing, card-games, cooking
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, pink, purple, amber
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, juice, mirinda
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, subway, tram, trike
 1. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1
 2. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 3. the person traveling to berlin is the person who likes amber##1
 4. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
 5. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
 6. the person driving the trike is the person traveling to berlin##1
 7. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
 8. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 9. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person who likes pink##1
10. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
11. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
12. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3    |       4       |
| City          | rome    | prague      | berlin  | hamburg   |
| Hobby   | cooking     | card-games      | writing | video-games      |
| Color           | pink       | blood-red         | amber  | purple         |
| Beverage         | cola | fanta | juice  | mirinda |
| Transport     | tram       | bike         | trike   | subway        |

