.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, soy-milk, sprite
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, skateboarding, badminton, surfing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, thriller, romance
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, card-games, puzzles, writing
House: craftsman, modern, palace, cape-cod
 1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 2. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the modern house##1
 3. the modern house is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
 4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far right##1
 5. the craftsman house is on the far left##1
 6. the palace house is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 7. the person watching romance movies is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
 9. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
10. the person drinking coffee is on the far right##1
11. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left##1
12. the cape-cod house is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk   | sprite   | cola      | coffee     |
| Sport          | badminton     | weightlifting   | surfing | skateboarding |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | thriller | disaster   | romance       |
| Hobby           | card-games       | cooking      | writing     | puzzles |
| House     | craftsman    | palace     | cape-cod     | modern     |

