11. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the fan of funk##1
12. the journalist is on the far left##1
13. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
14. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1

.:: Answer ::.
