 6. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person eating lime##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in august is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 8. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
 9. the person traveling to prague is on the far right##1
10. the person who's sport is rugby is the person who's birthday is in october##1
11. the person eating pomegranate is the person who likes aquamarine##1
12. the person traveling to paris is the person who's birthday is in february##1

