House: modern, townhouse, ranch-style, cottage
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, jet-ski, roller, trike
 1. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
 2. the fan of salsa is on the far left##1
 3. the person driving the airplane is the ranch-style house##1
 4. the person who growsiris is on the far left##1
 5. the fonseca-smoker is the townhouse house##1
 6. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person driving the trike##1
 7. the fan of funk is the person driving the jet-ski##1
 8. the person who growslily is the pall-mall-smoker##1
 9. the fan of metal is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
10. the modern house is the person who growsiris##1
11. the blend-smoker is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
12. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
13. the person who growslily is on the right of the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |      3       |       4       |
| Flower    | iris        | lily       | sunflower         | balloon-flower |
| Music-Genre       | salsa       | funk | metal      | punk     |
