.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-17::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, july, february, june
There are 4 different favourite colors: amber, black, brown, grey
The people have 4 different jobs:  firefighter, fisherman, photographer, security-guard
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, rock, country, electronic
4 different games are played: backgammon, chess, go, domino
 1. the fan of country is on the right of the firefighter##1
 2. the person who likes amber is the firefighter##1
 3. the fan of pop is on the left of the security-guard##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
 5. the person playing domino is on the far right##1
 6. the person who likes brown is on the far left##1
 7. the security-guard is on the left of the fan of rock##1
 8. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the fisherman##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in april is the person playing chess##1
10. the person who's birthday is in june is the fan of rock##1
11. the person playing go is on the left of the person who likes black##1
12. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |       2        |      3      |      4       |
| Birthday    | april     | july  | june       | february      |
| Color       | brown    | grey        | amber  | black      |
| Job         | fisherman  | security-guard | firefighter | photographer |
| Music-Genre         | pop | electronic          | rock         | country      |
| Game   | chess     | backgammon     | go       | domino          |

