.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-18::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, old-henry, havana, alhambra
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, september, june, february
There are 4 different favourite colors: lilac, aquamarine, green, coral
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, british, indonesian, mexican
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, van, jet-ski, airplane
 1. the indonesian is on the far left##1
 2. the old-henry-smoker is the person who likes coral##1
 3. the havana-smoker is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
 4. the mexican is on the left of the brazilian##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in june is the havana-smoker##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in february is the alhambra-smoker##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
 8. the brazilian is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
 9. the person driving the van is the person who likes green##1
10. the person who likes green is on the far left##1
11. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
12. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |      3       |    4     |
| Cigar      | alhambra       | havana      | old-henry      | bolivar    |
| Birthday         | february | june | september | may  |
| Color   | green    | aquamarine     | coral      | lilac |
| Nationality   | indonesian  | mexican     | brazilian    | british  |
| Transport           | van  | airplane       | roller          | jet-ski      |

