.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-19::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, tiparillo, ritmeester, davidoff
City: edinburgh, hamburg, london, rome
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, cola, 7up, fanta
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, parkour, rowing, skiing
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, september, january, june
 1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far left##1
 2. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in january is the person traveling to london##1
 4. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
 5. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 6. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
 8. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
 9. the person drinking cola is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
10. the person who's sport is skiing is the ritmeester-smoker##1
11. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
12. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far right##1
13. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |      3      |       4       |
| Cigar          | davidoff      | tiparillo     | baccarat        | ritmeester     |
| City         | london     | edinburgh    | rome | hamburg |
| Beverage   | mirinda | 7up  | cola      | fanta       |
| Sport         | rowing      | lacrosse | parkour     | skiing        |
| Birthday     | january   | june     | august  | september       |

