.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-20::.
There 4 different types of food: apricot, asparagus, cherry, grapes
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, old-henry, blend, tiparillo
There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, coral, brown, yellow
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, spy, drama, romance
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, blues, reggae, r&b
 1. the person who likes yellow is the dunhill-smoker##1
 2. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
 3. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
 4. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
 5. the person watching drama movies is the tiparillo-smoker##1
 6. the person eating cherry is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
 7. the fan of blues is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
 8. the person who likes light-blue is the fan of indie##1
 9. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
10. the person eating grapes is the person watching romance movies##1
11. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
12. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person who likes brown##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |       3        |      4      |
| Food        | asparagus    | grapes        | apricot        | cherry      |
| Cigar       | blend       | dunhill       | old-henry      | tiparillo |
| Color         | coral | yellow | brown | light-blue      |
| Movie-Genre         | sports          | romance         | spy           | drama    |
| Music-Genre   | reggae         | blues       | r&b     | indie   |

 